title_bed_bats_review: Tent in Joydebpur · 5 bedrooms · 8 beds · 2 baths
listing_description:
Reconnect with nature at this unforgettable MARS Village Camp (MVC), a camping site located just 90 minutes drive from Dhaka. This tranquil oasis offers a peaceful ambience surrounded by lush greenery.

MVC features 4 tents with beds, table and cupboard. Activists  like badminton, dart, carrom,  fishing are available. Facilities also include BBQ, both indoor & outdoor dining. 

MVC is a secured compound with 5  parking space. Experience the joy of camping where nature and comfort come together.

listing_description:
Welcome to our 375 sq. ft studio apartment

✦ We provide Airport drop off and Pick up for $15

✦ Our building consists of many amenities:
* Swimming pool
* Multi-purpose hall with stage
* Movie theatre (50 seats)
* Prayer room
* Fully equipped Gym
* Steam room
* Rooftop BBQ station
* Jogging track and rooftop gardens with seating
* Lounge area
* 24/7 Security

✦ We also provide:
* Room and bathroom cleaning
* Laundry Services
* Garbage collection
* Food (menu will be provided) 

Have a nice stay
